column5: Spinnerbaits & Crankbaits it was were windy & fairly rough but a good day
Nice job!  Was this Bass Lake Orillia? If so, congrads on getting them on those other baits, we could only get them on tubes last season.  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
Provincial Park At Orillia Lmbass were at the far end and horth west corner and Smallies were straight across from park along front of cottages 5 to 8 feet Richard
